  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094123/pizza-amalfi-coast-838x330.jpg?width=209&amp;height=21" alt="appetising walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/550c3eea615d4c278b578d23452fbbb0" /></p>
<p>Get a taste of Europe on our walking holidays. We’re not only here for the sights, but for the local flavours too! After a day of moving your feet, you deserve a culinary treat. Whether you’re eating in one of our family-run hotels enjoying delicious, traditional homemade meals, or dining out at one of the many local restaurants and cafés, there’s plenty to keep your taste buds happy.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2>Top destinations for food lovers</h2>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">Satisfy your taste buds as you stroll through stunning landscapes and savour the delicious flavours of local cuisine. Soak up the ambiance of each destination and raise a glass as you enjoy the ultimate foodie adventure!</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13102410/adobestock_226545684.jpg?width=500&amp;height=301" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/f4416e1993954b109adcabe731b9be2d" /></div>
<div class="c-card__content">
<h3><strong>Vienna, Austria</strong></h3>
<p><strong>Best for</strong> city and vineyard strolls, culture, food and wine</p>
<p><strong>What our experts say...</strong></p>
<p>If you love food, then you'll love Vienna. The city has a great variety of restaurants offering traditional Austrian cuisine, as well as other types of food from around the world. We recommend trying a slice of Sachertorte cake and sampling some fine Austrian wine.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094143/switzerlandpng.jpg?width=146&amp;height=21" alt="Davos Switzerland" data-udi="umb://media/10ec4b62279d4b9dbc8eef1b60ce8245" /></div>
<div class="c-card__content">
<h3><strong>Davos, Switzerland</strong></h3>
<p><strong>Best for</strong> traditional mountain huts, all levels of walks</p>
<p><strong>What our experts say...</strong></p>
<p>The food in Davos is hearty and authentic, with plenty of traditional Swiss fare. High up in the mountains, the huts provide a welcome break during your walk and there’s plenty of them to try, from devouring a fondue at the Stafelalp, to discovering the 450 year old Bergführer restaurant in the Sertigtal which is set amongst a spectacular mountain backdrop.</p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list c-card__cta-list--stacked"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094142/francepng.jpg?width=107&amp;height=21" alt="France liquer" data-udi="umb://media/0538ef1879414a09a82314dec5995c71" /></div>
<div class="c-card__content">
<h3><strong>Lake Annecy, France</strong></h3>
<p><strong>Best for</strong> lakeside views, easy and moderate walks, shopping, food lovers</p>
<p><strong>What our experts say...</strong></p>
<p>Lake Annecy is a haven for foodies, and has a fantastic choice of places to eat, from friendly cafes, to glamorous Michelin star restaurants. Try the alpine liqueur Génépi which is flavoured with various alpine herbs and plants. If you’re a cheese lover you can’t miss the delicious mountain cheeses here, the town’s full of artisan cheese shops so you’ll be spoilt for choice.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Foodie stays: Our favourite hotels</h2>
<p>Get ready to savour a delightful taste of Europe at these top hotels. Their menus offer a variety of cuisines, from regional specialties to international favourites.</p>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/a1afa31faaf14280a961bba40a1a2317" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1afa31faaf14280a961bba40a1a2317}" title="Hotel Schloss Lebenberg"><strong>Schloss Lebenberg, Austria</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13086533/schloss-lebenburg-kitzbuhel-restaurant3.jpg?width=181&amp;height=21" alt="schloss lebenberg hotel" data-udi="umb://media/9018d6f3d0a648b6945a6704fb56315a" /></p>
<p>Fancy some indulgent dining? This hotel offers a variety of international and regional dishes all expertly cooked and served in a stylish restaurant. </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/cd318f0b6b664b1b9e19cfaefeca536e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cd318f0b6b664b1b9e19cfaefeca536e}" title="Gardenhotel Theresia (Hinterglemm)">Gardenhotel Theresia, Austria</a></strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13083305/2019-12-gartenhotel-theresia-wintershooting-1649-min.jpg?width=162&amp;height=21" alt="gardenhotel theresia" data-udi="umb://media/e5aa3b438c0c4144bb269a8b086a506c" /></p>
<p>With a choice of three restaurants, the Gardenhotel offers a delightful culinary experience, with organically-certified fine cuisine for meat and fish lovers as well as vegetarian and vegan guests.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/c0cd670ad24d4d409a4f1331a1677937" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0cd670ad24d4d409a4f1331a1677937}" title="Hotel Belvedere"><strong>Hotel Belvedere, Switzerland</strong></a></p>
<p><strong><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13077906/essen-food-22_restaurant-belvedere-swiss-quality-hotel-grindelwald.jpg?width=138&amp;height=21" alt="hotel belvedere" data-udi="umb://media/8c22d33bcc624e6fa00b0d879b71e017" /></strong></p>
<p>The hotel restaurant serves a wide variety of gourmet food, with inventive cuisine and many fresh, homegrown ingredients used to create Swiss specialties with a light Mediterranean influence. </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/77d6333082dd4d6baa6fefd1170247eb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/77d6333082dd4d6baa6fefd1170247eb}" title="Hotel Miramare &amp; Spa">Hotel Miramare and Spa, Italy</a></strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094119/hotel_miramare_breakfast-1.jpg?width=124&amp;height=21" alt="hotel miramare" data-udi="umb://media/bea40a31ea7d46c9907f1ed649743934" /></p>
<p>The hotel’s Baia del Silenzio restaurant features in the Michelin Guide, and offers Ligurian cuisine using seasonal produce, classically prepared cuts of meat and fresh fish specials. </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/c5dd265c09ad472cb8a06e50409e10d7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5dd265c09ad472cb8a06e50409e10d7}" title="Hotel Grivola"><strong>Hotel Grivola, Italy</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13093597/2d7a2556.jpg?width=103&amp;height=21" alt="hotel grivola" data-udi="umb://media/30acf3cd45964cc4a981b73f69149340" /></p>
<p>Breakfast, lunch and dinner are served at this hotel. Breakfast is a buffet with hot and cold options, followed by a three-course meal in the restaurants every night. </p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
